name: Workshirty
tag_list: e-commerce, online, retail, business-shirts, online-retail, mens-clothing
overview:
Workshirty is here to provide young male professionals with a better fitting business shirt at a much lower cost than its competitors.They are a web driven retailer and work directly with factories to provide great quality corporate wear direct to the end customer.

The founder Dion Robeson was annoyed with paying high prices for his Monday to Friday corporate wear so he used his sourcing skills to produce the ultimate business shirt himself. Founded in the second half of 2011 Workshirty has a tight range of business shirts that are tailored to its target market.

Workshirty has started at the humble shirt; but our plans are much bigger. Quality corporate wear will be our game and providing this at a reasonable price is easy for us to do.
